Class StackBadia

  • java.lang.Object
    • StackBadia

  • public class StackBadia
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Alex Badia This is a class that creates a stack with an array where cards can be added (pushed) or removed (popped) from the stack. Other methods include isEmpty and isFull which indicate if the stack is empty or not and full or not full, respectively.
